If you know anything about Texas BBQ, this is the real deal.  Brisket and ribs, served by the pound - "yeh, cut me off a couple more slices of that brisket!"  Wonderful service and true Texas BBQ ambience.  This is no "chain".  Bring your friends, bring your visitors (hell, bring your cousin).  I'll be back!
BBQ at Luling is always a real treat. Their sausage is very meaty and brisket just delicious.
Extremely good barbecue. Really enjoyed the laid-back atmosphere and great service. It was nice to have barbeque that's not like everybody else.
